<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Gravel" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Gravel,</orth> subst. 1) small pebbles, hard sand: <cit><quote>when we see each grain of g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 1.1.155" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 1, 155</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>O g. heart,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 4.3.68" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 3, 68</bibl></cit> (== flint heart).<lb />2) a disease: <cit><quote>loads o' g. in the back,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 1, 22</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>